settings.description: Esquiva la balas y no te resvales en el hielo, buena suerte.
Fed up with Mario beating them up time and time again, all of the enemies turn giganto! Use the starman to blast your way through these larger-than-life foes.
REISSUE: Mario's least threatening foes have come together to create insanity in the sewers. Prod. Code: 105, Rel: 5/25/22 -- 8:56 am. I had no new levels finished, so I'm just pushing this out.

Just keep running, and don't stop! Let the triangular blocks guide you!
Difficulty: 2/5
Use the P-wing to dodge the spikes! One mess up and you are dead!

Help the penguin get to its' home by using invisible blocks and other gizmos. Friend request. :) 

Also included is a test room for the directional lift -- it's inclusion was canned b/c it didn't warp
Flutters fly across the sky and Wigglers are bound on ground in this simple nighttime course.
